<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10074270676892></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10074270676892><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=6&mid=10074270676892>RE: Paladins</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=6&mid=10074270676892#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=59305><span id=Scholar>Fennyin</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>100 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Dec 3rd 7:51 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.99]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think the main problem with paladins has nothing to do with paladins themselves... it's just that people don't know how to use them or are too insecure to be in a group without cleric-chanter-warrior.<br><br>This is just from my personal experience however, it may be different once I get up around 55 or so...<br><br><br>Examples of not knowing how to use us: <br><br>Cleric has 10% mana, we're about to take a med break.&nbsp;&nbsp;I'm at 80% health.  I cast Divine Purpose and have a seat.  Cleric gets up and uses last tiny bit of mana to heal me.<br><br>Ranger casts Skin Like Whatever on me as I'm healing myself with my DW helm.<br><br><br>Examples of insecurity:<br><br>I join a group along with a shaman, bard, druid, warrior, and mage.  Or something like that, but there was at least a shaman, bard, and druid.  Druid says that I need to leave because they need a cleric before they can fight anything.  Now obviously there's more than enough healing (3 healers plus a bard) and damage prevention (slow, stun, etc.) to keep the group alive...<br><br>Heard while running through North Ro: Soandso shouts, &quot;Derv 2 needs a cleric.&quot;<br>&nbsp;<br>Fennyin Ellies, Level 52 High Elf Cavalier<br>Terris-Thule Server</td></tr>
